data.description:
Incredible home in Bishop Arts on an oversized triangular lot. You are right in the center of everything Oak Cliff her to offer. Family home built brick brick made for outdoor entertainment, large gatherings, and family fun, OR, can you see yourself retiring here? This three bedroom, 2 bathroom home has two family areas,  an open concept space, and two outdoor living spaces. Plenty of covered parking that comfortably holds six cars or three large vehicles with additional parking available surrounding either side of the property. Newer roof, HVAC system, dish washer, and hot water heater. This home creates an oasis on your own corner surrounded by the Dallas city lights within walking distance of the Bishop Arts District. Where else can you find a home that gives you privacy in the city with a view of the stars, and be on vacation every day? This home is very unique, don't miss this opportunity.
Pictures coming soon
